  3.7820462387722845`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"a4de793a-8354-4836-ae4f-\
1e5334b6957a"],

Cell["\<\
You might have noticed that training the neural network predictor took \
significantly longer than training a predictor using the linear regression \
method. 

In order to compare, let us train a predictor using the linear regression \
method:\
\>", "Text",
