Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Overfitting", "Subsubsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.782048048942109*^9, 
  3.7820480506186523`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"35cf9346-6596-4143-a541-\
f10f09b0da7d"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Using a very deep network might look fashionable given the appeal of deep \
learning and might work well sometimes.\n\nHowever, by using many layers, we \
might end up overfitting unless we have a big enough dataset.",
 StyleBox["\n \nOverfitting",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 " is the failure of a model to generalize to data outside of the training \
set.\n\nIn the previous example, using a deeper network seems to adapt better \
to the particular fluctuations of the dataset. However, if we increase the \
size of the dataset, predictions might not be reliable to the model with many \
layers."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7820480626951823`*^9, 3.7820483191877856`*^9}, {
   3.7820486153473883`*^9, 3.782048616599608*^9}, {3.782048754404279*^9, 
   3.782048807766198*^9}, 3.7821459283017845`*^9, {3.815030073224456*^9, 
   3.815030116310602*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"1d277660-1d4d-4e80-bcbd-\
b45b8c1675eb"]
}, Open  ]]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Automated classification with Neural networks", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7800221922404776`*^9, 3.7800222017912254`*^9}, {
  3.780051366611409*^9, 
  3.7800513839637327`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"68e3ba3b-652d-45d1-92a7-\
45de8f21e2ad"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "The ",
 StyleBox["Classify", "CodeText"],
 " function can be used to automatically train a neural network to predict \
classes.\n\nFeel free to go through this subsection yourself. It is similar \
to the previous subsection on prediction but now dealing with classification."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.780021164826894*^9, 3.7800211663616176`*^9}, {
  3.7817763483361073`*^9, 3.7817763843212996`*^9}, {3.782048829006328*^9, 
  3.782048878999057*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"a69eb2b8-12f3-4811-baad-\
92e098dfaf28"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"c", "=", 
  RowBox[{"Classify", "[", 
   RowBox[{
