Cell["\<\
The panel \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]Learning curves for all algorithms\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] gives the loss function. The final value can be seen \
looking at the mean cross entropy which is the loss function used to train \
the ANN. \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8150321592114677`*^9, 
  3.8150322467329354`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"3f1f41d1-d6eb-4f61-b652-\
