Cell["\<\
Let us train a net with four outputs from a linear layer modified by a \
logistic activation function:\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7821943939193554`*^9, 3.782194420199888*^9}, {
  3.7821944797904787`*^9, 
